/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbGrGOUe.jpg&h=008e8d63&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n除咗後面嗰個，前面都係假，參考正常人推車<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t2RfTn3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft2RfTn3.jpg&h=86656090&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n1. 帶頭盔條腰直一直，根本發唔到力<br />\n<br />\n2. 全部人手勢都錯(紅圈) ，正常要發到力，左右手闊度要膊頭一樣，佢地成班左手搭右手，一個人推出力仲大<br />\n<br />\n3. 帶頭盔右手邊條友，佢推車方向絕對想謀殺<br />\n<br />\n結論，成班人大合照<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f10eae2d312c19d7a6695ef2754dcd9e06df0724","tid":2181393,"uid":83323,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T01:34:55.000Z","msg":"用後波唔得？ 同埋車入面條友做乜 <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yyOYReA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyyOYReA.png&h=5e5d1d62&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2187aa5474e9ab05498d179163c6b3175ca60ed3","tid":2181393,"uid":46700,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T01:41:29.000Z","msg":"其實消防到左就唔洗用呢種方法架<br />\n班狗係唔係睇太多美國戲以為自己係超人<br />\n而且睇落冇人固定架車<br />\n一陣班狗冇食禁藥手軟架車再跌返去前邊<br />\n個司機雖然受傷緊都會畀狗告老不啦<br />\n仲要畀人告多樣虐畜啦"},{"pid":"34a7fa57623d150e107217bf358f9915a12a6efd","tid":2181393,"uid":180404,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T01:57:07.000Z","msg":"黎黎黎<br />\n埋位影相"},{"pid":"3dde03b914b97370733658a9d4239fead8e46b13","tid":2181393,"uid":280648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T01:59:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f306bbb2f181ef1ddeb61eadc18e7990d4ecb0c","tid":2181393,"uid":188805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T02:18:10.000Z","msg":"就黎幫阿婆執籃球<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40ca485a4edb3e64e30171240fd217a7d19a9ae2","tid":2181393,"uid":146055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5117b415b1cb